*Baka* je pravljenje čarapa za decu. (Grandma was knitting socks for the children.)

*Bakom* je obožavala da se igra sa svojom decom. (Grandma loved to play with her children.)

*Baki* je rekao da je vreme da se ide kući. (Grandpa said that it was time to go home.)

*Bake* su volele da puštaju decu da se šeta po dvorištu. (Grandmas liked to let the children walk around the backyard.)

*Baku* su deca volela da posetuju. (The children liked to visit Grandma.)